title: Rory & Paddy's Great British Adventure
overview: Comedians Rory McGrath and Paddy McGuinness travel the UK in a camper van in search of strange sporting events. Their first stop is Gloucestershire, where they take part in the world-famous cheese rolling race. In the Cotswolds, Paddy tries his hand at river football, while Rory heads to Cambridge to get a crash course in tiddlywinks.
